<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.6">
<l>paṭainiṉ ṟapaintā maraiyō ṭaṇinīlam</l>
<l>maṭainiṉ ṟalarum vayalā limaṇāḷā</l>
<l>viṭaiya ṉeṟinta maramē yottirāmē</l>
<l>yaṭaiya varuḷā yeṉakkuṉ ṟaṉaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Master of Āli with fields where beautiful blue lilies and fresh lotuses</l>
<l>Which withstood the plough grow, remaining in channels,</l>
<l>Bestow your grace to me, in order to reach [you]</l>
<l>Without [my] being like a tree hacked at by herders.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
